{"tid":838419,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"百年廟宇染紅　變大陸愛國基地 台出動17挖泥機　拆「共產」禪寺","createTime":"2018-09-27T06:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T13:45:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":140,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"1f41eeafa39aa0254a3a3996644a68d080ce9466","tid":838419,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:01:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180927/20509040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F20509040&d=qy6Ry%2FISLpotfIeQJdc3d1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=7f39f803\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F20509040&h=715c3d5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180927/20509040</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月27日 <br />\n<br />\n百年廟宇染紅　變大陸愛國基地<br />\n台出動17挖泥機　拆「共產」禪寺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180927/large/a1601a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180927%2Flarge%2Fa1601a.gif&h=a1037152&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彰化縣政府進行清拆工作，挖泥機搗毀碧雲禪寺涉嫌僭建部份。台灣《蘋果日報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被稱為「共產基地」的台灣彰化縣碧雲禪寺，因涉嫌僭建被政府取締。彰化縣政府昨日展開大規模拆廟工作，其間出動600警力維持秩序，17部挖泥機前後夾攻，直接拆毀違建物，3小時就將「染紅」寺廟埋在瓦礫中，預計清拆工程為期一星期。大陸國台辦首次批評，拆廟暴露出民進黨放任縱容台獨分裂行徑，同時打擊主張統一的台灣人士。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180927/large/a1601b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180927%2Flarge%2Fa1601b.gif&h=2f8c76b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n10多部挖泥機前後夾擊拆廟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180927/large/a1601c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180927%2Flarge%2Fa1601c.gif&h=e326762f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工人抬出多個煤氣罐。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有將近百年歷史的彰化縣二水鄉碧雲禪寺，多年前爆發糾紛，商人魏明仁取得寺廟產權後，更名為「中華人民共和國台灣省社會主義民族思想愛國教育基地」，寺內法器與墨寶被中共宣傳海報、毛澤東與周恩來畫像取代，五星紅旗飄揚在外。美國《紐約時報》形容被紅海淹沒的碧雲禪寺是「奢華的中國共產黨朝聖地」。隨着該寺被投訴涉僭建，彰化縣長魏明谷早前決定先斷水斷電，再取締清拆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180927/large/a1601d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180927%2Flarge%2Fa1601d.gif&h=e9e37f36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中共支持者持五星旗離開碧雲禪寺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180927/large/a1601e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180927%2Flarge%2Fa1601e.gif&h=25497fa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n魏明仁與支持者昨到場升旗後離去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n600警力戒備<br />\n<br />\n縣政府昨早10時展開清拆工作，僭建面積超過1,700坪（約6萬平方呎），17部挖泥機在現場就位，為防示威者激烈抗爭，當局派遣600警力戒備，消防局與救護車派人支援。清拆開始前，魏明仁與不到10名支持者，在廟外匆匆升五星紅旗後立即降旗，隨後不發一言離開。<br />\n<br />\n建設處與警方不久後入廟檢查，確認無人及將汽油、煤氣罐及發電機等物品搬出後，挖泥機在寺廟前後同步拆廟。原本懸掛五星紅旗的旗竿最先被拆，樓梯被破壞，3小時後大廳被夷平。拆除後的磚塊、水泥會通知魏明仁清理，拆除費用500萬新台幣(約118萬港元)亦將由魏承擔。而當初失去碧雲禪寺產權，如今在寺旁搭鐵皮屋居住的尼姑，眼見寺廟被拆百感交集，希望未來能合法重建碧雲禪寺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被指危害國安<br />\n<br />\n彰化縣長魏明谷昨日在fb發文點出拆廟三大原因，包括魏明仁以手段取得建物、寺廟被當成中共愛國基地傷害台灣大眾感情、對國安構成危害。內政部長徐國勇表示，曾獲告知有人假藉宗教名義破壞治安，無論如何違建該拆就拆。大陸國台辦發言人安峰山昨在記者會上批評，事件暴露出民進黨一邊放任縱容「台獨」分裂行徑，一邊打擊和迫害主張統一的台灣人士，做法必將受到兩岸民眾的共同反對和譴責。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n王毅晤基辛格　籲中美棄冷戰思維<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n國民黨人變親共統派　升五星旗"},{"pid":"9fdcf5654b638dada86cf2b40545a4ff5fc51089","tid":838419,"uid":143499,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"應該用返蔣介石嗰套，共匪要打靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489c0a58c05b3e62bf96a034c60805d03f8c3356","tid":838419,"uid":98386,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:41:53.000Z","msg":"睇到強拆支共應該好有感先係 佢地最鍾意強拆民宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9dcc15c81462e61476ce5511da674445e2c6e3","tid":838419,"uid":51057,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:45:13.000Z","msg":"今次真係共&quot;剷&quot;廟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca474c324eef4c8452bd2fc061bfec3eda1b9563","tid":838419,"uid":41500,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清拆開始前，魏明仁與不到10名支持者，在廟外匆匆升五星紅旗後立即降旗，隨後不發一言離開。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做乜唔死守到底,力戰至最後一刻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係愛黨既,捐軀都要上啦,呢班所謂中國人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f37c99fe62262d7d1d879f020d1e73709668762","tid":838419,"uid":45376,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:58:54.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n小支支自己都好鍾意拆耶教教堂啦<br />\n出乜野聲啫"},{"pid":"ca981a793ec68e63ba16580e981489b375b8a946","tid":838419,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T07:19:42.000Z","msg":"拆僭建=台獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c3da022956fd5ca106a54302b3223f933523cd","tid":838419,"uid":53577,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9fdcf5654b638dada86cf2b40545a4ff5fc51089","tid":838419,"uid":143499,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"應該用返蔣介石嗰套，共匪要打靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg